{"tid":1678394,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人為咗返工而讀書？","createTime":"2019-10-27T15:45:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T05:44:46.000Z","uid":191093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5a6ba3dfa8b6ccac15bd9b844679487d31b03eb3","tid":1678394,"uid":191093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T15:45:49.000Z","msg":"我唔係講緊幾日嘅workshop / seminar 或者幾個月短course，而係起碼一年以上。<br />\n唉個個禮拜都走去返學，又要做功課又要考試。<br />\n但我又唔會好勤力咁讀，不過又唔會讀唔到，合格以上少少咁，又唔會高分，但感覺唔會真係有好多嘢實質落到袋。<br />\n同埋就算當我好努力讀，記到全部理論，落曬袋，但我個行又實戰為主，同埋好睇trend，所以反而聽下啲一兩日seminar知道有咩update仲好。<br />\n好矛盾好迷惘，好似根本就係等時間過，夠鐘就拎張沙紙走。明白捱過咗就會順好多，但而家真係好忙好攰，都算，最慘係無個滿足感同實用性，唉。"},{"pid":"86bfefe744ab85caddfcb4cf0cc24f80cdd98b65","tid":1678394,"uid":191093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T15:52:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ea37f8d8b9d872ff8539cb9845e1d4e04c6ae31","tid":1678394,"uid":191093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T15:58:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62415a35b8b66bf3c035b0c6bacdb15a7b9b9fb4","tid":1678394,"uid":246943,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:04:04.000Z","msg":"同你有少少5同，做過兩年服務業，兒加全職學生，向MLT發展"},{"pid":"f2e4bd0fb6d6f1280ef14bd992293b8165facf2a","tid":1678394,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:05:34.000Z","msg":"乞食科Grad <br />\n做緊it related, 遲啲會轉返full time 讀second degree"},{"pid":"76cc81dadcf082e44df54137c2d5b795a96c1c46","tid":1678394,"uid":78576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T05:29:14.000Z","msg":"same <br />\n岩岩開始左讀 top up  degree <br />\n但英文底差 跟唔上 又多功課,多project 多present <br />\n都唔知合唔合格到...分分鐘要搵人幫手<br />\n有d想放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但又比左一舊錢<br />\n好迷惘好攰..."},{"pid":"519e1e31e8ec8c6d88af73d9be0e9abbdec2775f","tid":1678394,"uid":67765,"